questions.quote: Joey, what are you doing?! It's never gonna happen, she's seeing somebody.
Oh, it's just some crazy guy who roams the halls here. He's great with kids though.
Oh, no, no, no, no. You know what, he's not into that stuff anymore. He quit for me.
Hmm, something bad to tell Rachel... Bad news for Rachel, what could that be?!
Okay, my trainer, Ho Chi, is teaching me a combination of Gee Koon Doe and Brazilian street fighting, I've even had my own octagon training ring designed.
Phoebe?! Wait a-but-but she just, she said that Joey was her backup.
Okay, Joey, you know what? You have to go for it. How often does this happen to you, huh? You owe it to yourself.
Yes, this Russell, Ross's divorce lawyer, just tell him that since I haven't heard from him, I assume he's decided to give the marriage a try.
Okay, I'm gonna get your coat and then I'll-I'll put you in a cab.
Well, I-I still think you're very-very nice and very pretty...
